# Keep build contexts small and avoid copying host-specific artifacts (notably
# node_modules symlinks) into images. Deps are reinstalled from the lockfile.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/build
**/out
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.git
.github
.idea
.vscode
**/*.log
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
openspec
